quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  101,1,The Crashing Blow
  101,2,What is the Crashing Blow
  101,3,What will convey to you what the Crashing Blow is
  101,4,It is the Day when mankind will be like scattered moths
  101,5,and the mountains like tufts of coloured wool
  101,6,As for him whose balance is heavy
  101,7,he will have a most pleasant life
  101,8,But as for him whose balance is light
  101,9,his motherland is Hawiya
  101,10,And what will convey to you what that is
  101,11,A raging Fire